    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Invaders</h2>The asteroid-riding termites are back and trying to destroy all the space ants! Join the battle and defend multiple universes in this tiny yet epic adventure!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366290/extras/cde5d09bc443576eec2d1b8056809d9f.poster.avif?t=1766170779\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366290/extras/cde5d09bc443576eec2d1b8056809d9f.webm?t=1766170779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366290/extras/cde5d09bc443576eec2d1b8056809d9f.mp4?t=1766170779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exploration</h2>Navigate the dangerous depths of space and pilot your spacecraft full of ants.<br>Fly through unknown obstacles in search of valuable resources and the means to ensure your survival.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366290/extras/45ad6edeaa052b51b73383c290c2a1ad.poster.avif?t=1766170779\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366290/extras/45ad6edeaa052b51b73383c290c2a1ad.webm?t=1766170779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366290/extras/45ad6edeaa052b51b73383c290c2a1ad.mp4?t=1766170779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Managment and Strategy</h2>Explore, collect resources, and uncover secrets on uncharted planets. Build ant societies and overcome the challenges of the unknown.<br>Adapt to the challenges of diverse planets and biomes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366290/extras/e933d2ffc4330f94aa1ae9e33ef4f4d1.poster.avif?t=1766170779\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366290/extras/e933d2ffc4330f94aa1ae9e33ef4f4d1.webm?t=1766170779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366290/extras/e933d2ffc4330f94aa1ae9e33ef4f4d1.mp4?t=1766170779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combat</h2>Take part in intense, high-stakes battles with dangerous foes at every turn. You must carefully choose when to engage in combat or when to retreat to safety.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366290/extras/d657eeb151d7674a77ec5fb5046f3d85.poster.avif?t=1766170779\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366290/extras/d657eeb151d7674a77ec5fb5046f3d85.webm?t=1766170779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366290/extras/d657eeb151d7674a77ec5fb5046f3d85.mp4?t=1766170779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mixing Species!</h2>Experiment with DNA to create new, unique species with special abilities and traits. Watch as they change colours and shapes as you progress trough the vastness of space and conquer new territories.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366290/extras/756f42035f24a989ec8ec81f04a604b0.poster.avif?t=1766170779\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366290/extras/756f42035f24a989ec8ec81f0